WEBVTT

00:00.023 --> 00:01.351
Do it.

00:02.063 --> 00:03.633
I'm sorry.

00:06.633 --> 00:08.475
<i>I'll do the time.</i>

00:08.500 --> 00:10.267
You drive me to the police
station right now.

00:10.269 --> 00:12.669
- It's too late.
- I have to go now.

00:15.741 --> 00:17.808
<i>I think you and Des
have a little side business.</i>

00:18.844 --> 00:20.110
I want a cut.

00:20.112 --> 00:21.411
Everything's my fault
even though

00:21.413 --> 00:23.544
I'm the one who told you
to stay away from Grady!

00:23.569 --> 00:26.249
<i>I told you he came after my kid!</i>

00:26.251 --> 00:29.186
I couldn't live with myself
if I made a decision

00:29.188 --> 00:32.055
based on something he said
in a moment of fear.

00:32.057 --> 00:33.723
What should I do?

00:33.725 --> 00:36.760
<i>You think Grant is the son of
Lucas Grant, Judge Lucas Grant.</i>

00:36.762 --> 00:37.861
He could have done
a clinical trial.

00:37.863 --> 00:39.062
He could've done
a million things.

00:39.064 --> 00:41.598
What he could not have done
was give consent.

00:41.600 --> 00:42.966
She's going to say
you had sex, Ben.

00:42.968 --> 00:44.935
And no one is gonna believe her

00:44.937 --> 00:46.903
if we get rid of the tape.

00:46.905 --> 00:50.240
I was born sick, born broken.

00:50.242 --> 00:51.808
<i>So I met with Morgan.</i>

00:51.810 --> 00:53.643
He wants to wave the white flag.

00:54.780 --> 00:56.780
- Am I under arrest?
- Let's go.

00:56.782 --> 00:58.248
He wears a wire,
gathers evidence

00:58.250 --> 00:59.783
against his partner.

00:59.785 --> 01:01.118
We offer him immunity.

01:01.120 --> 01:02.986
We will get back to you.

01:02.988 --> 01:05.689
<i>Mary Mitchell,
now known as Mary Harris,</i>

01:05.691 --> 01:07.824
was investigated
for the murder of her mother.

01:07.826 --> 01:09.626
Her mother was found dead
in Chalk Lake

01:09.628 --> 01:11.294
with her hands tied together.

01:11.296 --> 01:13.163
<i>Man, you don't know
who this woman is.</i>

01:13.165 --> 01:14.464
<i>She's been involved in the death</i>

01:14.466 --> 01:16.099
<i>of God knows how many people.</i>

01:16.101 --> 01:18.186
Am I crazy like Mom?

01:24.910 --> 01:27.144
<i>Why are you doing this?</i>

01:27.146 --> 01:28.411
<i>What?</i>

01:28.413 --> 01:30.780
<i>Saving people
a trip to Switzerland.</i>

01:30.782 --> 01:32.516
<i>I believe</i>

01:32.518 --> 01:35.285
<i>we should be in control
of our life and our death.</i>

01:35.287 --> 01:36.753
<i>That's liberty.</i>

01:36.755 --> 01:38.588
<i>And dying isn't a crime.</i>

01:38.590 --> 01:41.158
<i>But helping people die
makes you a criminal.</i>

01:41.160 --> 01:42.813
<i>You think so?</i>

01:44.963 --> 01:48.198
<i>I mean... yeah.</i>

01:52.304 --> 01:53.870
<i>Is there a long answer?</i>

01:53.872 --> 01:55.605
I should've come forward sooner.

01:55.607 --> 01:58.441
I know that now.

01:58.443 --> 02:02.045
I'd like to explain.

02:02.047 --> 02:04.514
I'm a doctor.
My patient was suffering.

02:04.516 --> 02:07.617
I couldn't just stand by
and do nothing.

02:14.026 --> 02:15.892
<i>God, you don't seem sick.</i>

02:20.732 --> 02:22.365
<i>I'm sorry.
I meant that as compliment.</i>

02:22.367 --> 02:25.335
I'm sorry.
I was acting on instinct.

